# Retail-AI

This is a basic Android project where it tried to build a small retail-related app with simple validation and user flow. The idea is to simulate how user data can be verified before moving ahead in an application.

---

## What this project does

* Takes user input (name and age)
* Validates the input
* Shows verification status
* Allows moving to next screen only after verification

---

## Tech used

* Kotlin
* Android Studio
* XML (for UI)
* Gradle

---

## How to run

1. Clone the repo:

   ```
   git clone https://github.com/HarShada8G/Retail-AI.git
   ```

2. Open in Android Studio

3. Run on emulator or real device

